2011年1月8日，[[美国众议院|美国联邦众议员]][[加布里埃尔·吉福兹|加布里埃尔·吉福兹]]在[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]][[图森_(亚利桑那州)|图森]]卡萨斯阿道比斯的一家超市[[停车场|停车场]]举行见面会时，和另外18人一起遭到枪击。这起事件导致包括[[美国亚利桑纳联邦地区法院|联邦地区法院]]首席法官[[約翰·羅爾|約翰·羅爾]]，吉福兹的随从加布·齐默尔曼（{{lang|en|Gabe Zimmerman}}）以及年仅9岁的女孩克里斯蒂娜-泰勒·格林（{{lang|en|Christina-Taylor Green}}）在内的6人丧生<ref name="azcentral2011-01-08-optimistic" /><ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09">{{cite news |last=Lacey |first=Marc |coauthors=David M. Herszenhorn |title=In Attack's Wake, Political Repercussions |date=2011-01-09 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09giffords.html |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605031613/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09giffords.html |archivedate=2013-06-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="CNN2011-01-08">{{cite news |publisher=CNN |title=Police 'actively pursuing' second person in Tucson shooting |date=2011-01-08 |url=http://us.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/08/arizona.shooting/ |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2012-04-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120403031133/http://articles.cnn.com/2011-01-08/justice/arizona.shooting_1_law-enforcement-source-federal-judge?_s=PM%3ACRIME }}</ref><ref name="complaint">{{cite news |archivedate=2012-03-15 |deadurl=no |url=http://documents.nytimes.com/criminal-complaint-against-jared-lee-loughner |title=Criminal Complaint Against Jared Lee Loughner |work=The New York Times |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315203618/http://documents.nytimes.com/criminal-complaint-against-jared-lee-loughner |accessdate=2011-01-18 }}</ref><ref name="CBS-20110110-linked">{{cite news |last=Couric |first=Katie |title=Strangers Linked by Tragedy in Tucson Rampage |publisher=CBS News |date=2011-01-10 |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/01/10/eveningnews/main7232620.shtml |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103061057/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2011/01/10/eveningnews/main7232620.shtml |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。吉福兹在这家[[西夫韦公司|西夫弗]]超市停车场主持的见面会名为“国会在你这边”，贾里德·李·劳纳掏出手枪先一枪打中了她的头部，然后开始朝其他人射击<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" /><ref name="CNN2011-01-08" />，此外还有一人在试图制服劳纳的过程中受伤<ref name="WP-20110114-victims" />。新闻报导称这次袭击以吉福兹为目标，她是代表亚利桑那州第8国会选区的[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]议员<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" />，子弹近距离打中她的头部后穿脑而过，病情起初“非常危急”<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" /><ref name="CNN2011-01-08" />。

22岁的劳纳是图森人，迷恋吉福兹，他被当场逮捕<ref name="Kanalley2011-01-08" />。联邦检察官对他发起了包括试图刺杀国会议员和联邦法官在内的五项控罪<ref name="complaint" /><ref name="I planned">{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |title=Suspect in Arizona massacre: 'I planned ahead' |date=2011-01-10 |newspaper=Chicago Sun-Times |url=http://www.suntimes.com/3228379-417/giffords-born-chances-commands-described.html |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2012-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009150812/http://www.suntimes.com/3228379-417/giffords-born-chances-commands-described.html }}</ref><ref name="Lacey2011-01-09">{{cite news |last=Lacey |first=Marc |title=Evidence Points to Methodical Planning |date=2011-01-09 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10giffords.html |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515174647/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10giffords.html |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。劳纳之前曾因[[毒品|毒品]]轻罪指控被捕，但没有定罪<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/articles/2011/01/09/20110109jared-lee-loughner-gabrielle-giffords-arizona-shooting.html |title=Jared Lee Loughner, suspect in Gabrielle Giffords shooting, had college run-ins |author=Robert Anglen |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |publisher=The Arizona Republic |work=azcentral.com}}</ref>，他还因破坏行为被大学暂停学业。法庭纪录中的劳纳手写笔记表明他策划刺杀吉福兹<ref name="I planned" />。枪击的动机尚未查明，劳纳调用[[沉默权|沉默权]]，拒绝与当局合作<ref name="CNN2011-01-08" />。他一共受到49项罪名起诉且不得保释。2012年1月，联邦法官根据两份医疗评估认为劳纳不能出庭受审，报告认为他患有[[偏執狂|偏执]][[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]]<ref name="competence">{{cite news |url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/25/judge-loughner-not-competent-to-stand-trial/ |title=Judge: Loughner not competent to stand trial in Arizona shootings |publisher=CNN |date=2011-05-25 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913181638/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/05/25/judge-loughner-not-competent-to-stand-trial/ |archivedate=2012-09-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，到了5月25日，法官仍然认为[[被告|被告]]不能受审。但8月7日举行的听证会裁定劳纳可以出庭。他对19项控罪认罪，于2012年11月被判终身监禁。

事件发生后，美国和国际社会的[[政治家|政治家]]表达了悲痛和谴责。一些评论家就此事指责政治右翼成员，特别是[[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]，因为她的演讲中有些与枪有关的隐喻，并且她的政治活动委员会网站上所配的图片还用[[瞄准镜|瞄准镜]]在选举地图上瞄准了吉福兹等人。另一些评论则认为劳纳是个仇视所有政客而不论其从属关系的[[无政府主义|无政府主义者]]，以此来为佩林辩护<ref name="rhetoric">{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-09/lawmakers-urge-end-to-political-rhetoric-after-tucson-shootings.html |title=Giffords Shooting in Arizona May Cool U.S. Political Rhetoric, Hurt Palin |first=Heidi |last=Przybyla |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |publisher=Bloomberg |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104103158/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-09/lawmakers-urge-end-to-political-rhetoric-after-tucson-shootings.html |archivedate=2012-11-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[槍枝管制|槍枝管制]]的倡导者主张对枪支和弹药，特别是大容量[[彈匣|彈匣]]的销售增加限制<ref name="gun_control">{{cite news |author=Tom Cohen |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/POLITICS/01/16/congress.gun.control/index.html |title=Democrats face tough fight on gun control after Tucson shootings |date=2011-01-17 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110121222002/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/POLITICS/01/16/congress.gun.control/index.html |archivedate=2011-01-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[美国总统|美国总统]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]于1月12日主持全国直播的悼念仪式，此外美国各地还举行了其它多种纪念活动。

==枪击==
[[File:Gabrielle_Giffords_shooting_scene_2.jpg|thumb]]
枪击发生于2011年1月8日[[北美山区时区|MST]]早上10点10分（[[协调世界时|UTC]]17点10分）<ref name="Gillum-2011-01-14" /><ref name="NYT_Video">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/19/us/19giffords.html?_r=0 |title=Video Captured 'Calculated' Gunman in Tucson |author=Richard A. Oppel Jr. |work=The New York Times |date=2011-01-18 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409165146/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/19/us/19giffords.html |archivedate=2013-04-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。来自亚利桑那州的联邦众议员加布里埃尔·吉福兹正在该州[[图森_(亚利桑那州)|图森]]北部[[非建制地區|非建制地區]]卡萨斯阿道比斯的一家西夫韦[[超市|超市]]停车场举行一场名为“国会在你这边”的会面活动<ref name="Lacey2011-01-09" /><ref name="NYT_Dolnick">{{cite news |last=Dolnick |first=Sam |title=Flashbacks and Lingering Questions for Survivors |date=2011-01-12 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13survivors.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409165150/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13survivors.html |archivedate=2013-04-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Routine event turned deadly fast |agency=Los Angeles Times, The New York Times |newspaper=Star Tribune |location=Minneapolis – Saint Paul |date=2011-01-10 |archivedate=2012-10-15 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.startribune.com/nation/113181349.html |accessdate=2013-10-06 |quote=She and an aide parked an SUV in the lot of La Toscana Village, a mall about 8 miles north of downtown Tucson. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015225901/http://www.startribune.com/nation/113181349.html }}</ref>。吉福兹在商店外设立了一张桌台，贾里德·李·劳纳掏出[[手枪|手枪]]打中她的头部时，有20到30人聚集在她周围<ref name="AZRepublic-20110112-visits">{{cite news |last=Alltucker |first=Ken |url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/articles/2011/01/12/20110112gabrielle-giffords-more-responsive-brk12-ON.html |title=Obama visits Giffords at hospital, leaves for speech on campus |newspaper=The Arizona Republic |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-06}}</ref><ref name="Lacey-Williams2011-01-13">{{cite news |last=Lacey |first=Marc |last2=Williams |first2=Timothy |title=Doctors Call Giffords's Progress Remarkable |date=2011-01-13 |newspaper=The New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/14/us/14giffords.html |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2013-08-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819133526/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/14/us/14giffords.html }}</ref>。商店的一个保安摄像头拍下了枪击案过程，但这段视频尚未对公众发布<ref name="NYT_Video" /><ref name="WashPost_video">{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/18/AR2011011801155.html |title=Videos show details of Tucson shooting |author=David Nakamura |coauthors=Dana Hedgpeth; Sari Horwitz |work=The Washington Post |date=2011-01-19 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210195126/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/18/AR2011011801155.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

劳纳显然是任意地朝人群中的其他人开火<ref name="azcentral2011-01-08-optimistic" /><ref name="Quinn-Gallagher-2011-01-09">{{cite news |last=Quinn |first=Ben |last2=Gallagher |first2=Paul |title=US congresswoman Gabrielle Giffords shot as six die in Arizona massacre |date=2011-01-09 |work=The Guardian |location=London |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/jan/08/gabrielle-giffords-shot-tucson-arizona |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501005156/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jan/08/gabrielle-giffords-shot-tucson-arizona |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。报导称他使用的是一支[[9×19mm魯格彈|9毫米]]口径格洛克19型[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]，配有可装33发子弹的弹匣<ref name="Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite news |url=http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/11_04/b4212052185280.htm |last=Barrett |first=Paul M. |title=Glock: America's Gun |date=2011-01-13 |work=Bloomberg Businessweek |publisher=Bloomberg L.P. |archivedate=2013-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821034718/http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/11_04/b4212052185280.htm |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref><ref name="SPTimes-20110114">{{cite news |last=DeGregory |first=Lane |url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/little-surprise-that-popular-glock-19-was-used-in-arizona-shooting/1145393 |title=Little surprise that popular Glock 19 was used in Arizona shooting |newspaper=St. Petersburg Times |date=2011-01-14 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2012-10-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014113129/http://www.tampabay.com/news/little-surprise-that-popular-glock-19-was-used-in-arizona-shooting/1145393 }}</ref>。附近一家商店的雇员称自己听到了“15到20声枪响”<ref name="NYPost-20110109-terror">{{cite news |last=Karni |first=Annie |archivedate=2012-10-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021194848/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/national/terror_then_eerie_calm_as_victims_P8wp5ziGYD09FsyNz9OS4M |url=http://nypost.com/2011/01/09/terror-then-eerie-calm-as-victims-fall/ |title=Terror, then eerie calm as victims fall |newspaper=New York Post |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>。劳纳停下来重新装弹，但口袋里的弹匣掉到了人行道上，在一旁看到的帕特里夏·迈施（{{lang|en|Patricia Maisch}}）抓到了弹匣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/09/arizona.shooting/index.html |title=Congresswoman's responses after Arizona shooting called encouraging |date=2011-01-09 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2013-02-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228091234/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/09/arizona.shooting/index.html }}</ref>。另一名旁观者用折叠椅打中了行凶者的后脑，并在这一过程中伤到了自己的手肘，成了第14名伤者<ref name="ABC-20110110-heroes">{{cite news |last=Hopper |first=Jessica |last2=Dolak |first2=Kevin |last3=Sher |first3=Lauren |title=Heroes of Tucson Shooting: 'Something Had to Be Done' |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/heroes-rep-gabrielle-giffords-shooting-tucson-arizona-subdued/story?id=12580345 |publisher=ABC News |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927011219/http://abcnews.go.com/US/heroes-rep-gabrielle-giffords-shooting-tucson-arizona-subdued/story?id=12580345 |archivedate=2013-09-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。劳纳随后被自己打中的74岁退伍[[美国陆军|美国陆军]][[上校|上校]]比尔·巴杰（{{lang|en|Bill Badger}}）扑倒在地<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wnep.com/wnep-schyl-man-tackled-az-gunman-schuylkill-ties,0,7811918.story |title=Man who Tackled AZ Gunman has Schuylkill County Ties |author=Renie Workman |date=2011-01-10 |publisher=WNEP-TV |accessdate=2012-03-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315072846/http://www.wnep.com/wnep-schyl-man-tackled-az-gunman-schuylkill-ties%2C0%2C7811918.story |archivedate=2012-03-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，再被迈施和另外两名旁观者罗杰·索兹格伯（{{lang|en|Roger Sulzgeber}}）和约瑟夫·萨穆迪奥（{{lang|en|Joseph Zamudio}}）制服。萨穆迪奥身上带有枪支，但等他到达现场时枪击已经停止，他也没有再取出武器<ref name="ABC_News_12577933">{{cite news |last=Dolak |first=Kevin |last2=Weaver |first2=Justin |title=Woman Wrestled Fresh Ammo Clip From Tucson Shooter as He Tried to Reload |publisher=ABC News |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/patricia-maisch-describes-stopping-gunman-reloading/story?id=12577933 |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130818130831/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/patricia-maisch-describes-stopping-gunman-reloading/story?id=12577933 |archivedate=2013-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。萨穆迪奥之后表示，自己起初将另一人错认为枪手并差点拔出枪来，但最后及时发现自己认错了人<ref name="Saletan">{{cite news |last=Saletan |first=William |title=Armed Giffords hero nearly shot wrong man |publisher=NBC News |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/41018893/ |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914001326/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/41018893/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

现场于上午10点11分打出了第一通紧急服务电话<ref name="Gillum-2011-01-14" />。在等待救援人员前来的过程中，吉福兹的[[实习|实习生]]小丹尼尔·埃尔南德斯（{{lang|en|Daniel Hernández, Jr.}}）对她前额上的枪伤施压，并确保她不会被自己的血呛住，他的行动挽救了吉福兹的生命<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-11-02 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.salon.com/life/feature/2011/01/10/daneil_hernandez_gay_latino_hero |journal=Salon |first=Mary Elizabeth |last=Williams |title=The Giffords shooting's gay, Hispanic hero |date=2011-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102115158/http://www.salon.com/2011/01/10/daneil_hernandez_gay_latino_hero/ |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://opinion.latimes.com/opinionla/2011/01/two-gay-heroes-thwart-assassinations-what-a-difference-35-years-make.html |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |first=Patt |last=Morrison |title=Two gay heroes thwart assassinations – what a difference 35 years make |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112190452/http://opinion.latimes.com/opinionla/2011/01/two-gay-heroes-thwart-assassinations-what-a-difference-35-years-make.html |archivedate=2011-01-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大卫·保曼（{{lang|en|David Bowman}}）和南茜·保曼（{{lang|en|Nancy Bowman}}）夫妇分别是[[医生|医生]]和[[护士|护士]]，他们正在商店内购物，两人立即开始[[分诊|分诊]]，并照料9岁的克里斯蒂娜-泰勒·格林<ref name="CBS-20110110-linked" />。警察于上午10点15分到达现场，医护人员则在一分钟后到达<ref name="abc15-911">{{cite news |url=http://www.abc15.com/dpp/news/region_central_southern_az/tucson/911-call%3A-%22i-do-believe-gabby-giffords-was-hit%22 |title=911 call: "I do believe Gabby Giffords was hit" |publisher=Abc15.com |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130320185658/http://www.abc15.com/dpp/news/region_central_southern_az/tucson/911-call%3A-%22i-do-believe-gabby-giffords-was-hit%22 |archivedate=2013-03-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。巴杰发现行凶者试图丢弃一个装有现金和证件的小包，之后警官们找到了这些物品<ref name="DoD-20110112">{{cite news |title=Retired Guard Member Helps Subdue Arizona Gunman |archivedate=2013-07-13 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.defense.gov/news/newsarticle.aspx?id=62420 |agency=American Forces Press Service |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130713155438/http://www.defense.gov/News/NewsArticle.aspx?ID=62420 }}</ref>。枪击发生后，警察关闭了购物中心周围的道路一段时间。整个周末进行初步调查期间，路口拉起了封锁线，购物中心的大部分商店都予关闭<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-07-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120702230514/http://explorernews.com/news/pima_pinal/article_0b9e3f99-f0dd-53e7-9392-061e76457aba.html |url=http://explorernews.com/news/pima_pinal/article_0b9e3f99-f0dd-53e7-9392-061e76457aba.html |title='Utter shock' -Area residents shaken but optimistic |work=The Explorer |author=Wendy Miller |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>。西夫韦商店于一个星期后重新开张，门口临时搭建了纪念场所<ref name="Safeway">{{cite web |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/41091483/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ |title=Giffords removed from respirator, has tracheotomy – Grocery store where shooting occurred reopens as Tucson |publisher=MSNBC |date=2011-01-15 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2012-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105123306/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/41091483/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ }}</ref>。枪击事件共造成5人在当场死亡<ref name="AZStar-20110108-killed">{{cite news |archivedate=2011-12-17 |deadurl=no |url=http://azstarnet.com/news/local/article_88b4b436-1b53-11e0-8354-001cc4c002e0.html |title=Rep. Giffords shot, judge and 5 others killed at Tucson event |newspaper=Arizona Daily Star |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111217000014/http://azstarnet.com/news/local/article_88b4b436-1b53-11e0-8354-001cc4c002e0.html }}</ref>，其中包括首席法官约翰·罗尔和吉福兹手下的社区外联主任加布·齐默尔曼<ref name="azcentral2011-01-08-optimistic" /><ref name="complaint" />。大部分伤者被送往图森大学医疗中心<ref name="EpochTimes-20110108-survives">{{cite news |last=Belmaker |first=Genevieve Long |coauthors=Belmaker, Gidon |archivedate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/united-states/gabrielle-giffords-survives-surgery-doctors-optimistic-48881.html |title=Gabrielle Giffords Survives Surgery, Doctors 'Optimistic' |newspaper=The Epoch Times |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009052311/http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/united-states/gabrielle-giffords-survives-surgery-doctors-optimistic-48881.html }}</ref>。克里斯蒂娜-泰勒·格林在送医院急救的路上被宣布[[到院前死亡|死亡]]<ref name="CNN2011-01-08" /><ref name="Gonzalez2011-01-08-victims">{{cite news |last=Gonzalez |first=Daniel |title=Arizona Congresswoman Gabrielle Giffords: The victims |date=2011-01-08 |newspaper=The Arizona Republic |url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/articles/2011/01/08/20110108arizona-congresswoman-gabrielle-giffords-shooting-victims-brk08-ON.html |accessdate=2013-10-06}}</ref>。

当劳纳的双亲回到家时，他们还不知道发生了枪击事件，两人看到了房子周围被警车和封锁线团团封锁。他们的[[邻居|邻居]]韦恩·史密斯（{{lang|en|Wayne Smith}}）称劳纳的[[母亲|母亲]]“差点当场昏过去”，而他的[[父亲|父亲]]则坐在路上痛哭。史密斯形容这个家庭被“摧毁”了，他们感到内疚并奇怪：“自己到底做错了什么？”<ref name="Stanglin2011-01-11">{{cite news |last=Stanglin |first=Douglas |archivedate=2012-10-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005134310/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/01/suspect-jared-loughners-parents-devastated-by-tucson-shootings/1#.UlFUIRY9Rug |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/01/suspect-jared-loughners-parents-devastated-by-tucson-shootings/1#.UlFUIRY9Rug |title=Suspect Jared Loughner's parents 'devastated' by Tucson shootings |work=USA Today |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>劳纳的父母在三天后发表了一份声明，向受害者表示自责，说“我们不明白为什么会发生这样的事情。”<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2012-10-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005134310/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/01/suspect-jared-loughners-parents-devastated-by-tucson-shootings/1 |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2011/01/11/father-arizona-shooting-rampage-suspect-speaks/ |title=Family of Arizona Shooting Rampage Breaks Silence, Expresses Remorse for Victims |publisher=Fox News Channel |date=2010-04-07 |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>

