==加布里埃尔·吉福兹==
[[File:Gabrielle_Giffords_official_portrait.jpg|thumb]]
报道称加布里埃尔·吉福兹是这次枪击事件的目标<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" />。一些新闻机构起初报道她被枪杀，但之后很快更正为从头部枪伤下生还<ref name="poynter_mistakes">{{cite web |last=Moos |first=Julie |title=After conflicting reports in Arizona shooting, Sklar, Silverman track media mistakes while NPR explains |url=http://www.poynter.org/latest-news/top-stories/113736/after-conflicting-reports-in-arizona-shooting-folkenflik-uses-twitter-to-explain-media-mistakes/ |publisher=Poynter Institute |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110110201233/http://www.poynter.org/latest-news/top-stories/113736/after-conflicting-reports-in-arizona-shooting-folkenflik-uses-twitter-to-explain-media-mistakes/ |archivedate=2011-01-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="politico_npr">{{cite news |last=Hagey |first=Keach |title=NPR: 'We regret the erroneous news' |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0111/47282.html |newspaper=Politico |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513045928/http://www.politico.com//news/stories/0111/47282.html |archivedate=2013-05-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。吉福兹的实习生小丹尼尔·埃尔南德斯在她受伤后进行了援助，并挽救了她的生命<ref name="Salon-20110110">{{cite news |last=Williams |first=Mary Elizabeth |url=http://www.salon.com/2011/01/10/daneil_hernandez_gay_latino_hero/ |title=The Giffords shooting's gay, Hispanic hero |journal=Salon |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102115158/http://www.salon.com/2011/01/10/daneil_hernandez_gay_latino_hero/ |archivedate=2012-11-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="LATimes-20110110">{{cite news |last=Morrison |first=Patt |url=http://opinion.latimes.com/opinionla/2011/01/two-gay-heroes-thwart-assassinations-what-a-difference-35-years-make.html |title=Two gay heroes thwart assassinations – what a difference 35 years make |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110114213856/http://opinion.latimes.com/opinionla/2011/01/two-gay-heroes-thwart-assassinations-what-a-difference-35-years-make.html |archivedate=2011-01-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Huffington-20110110">{{cite news |last=Foley |first=Elise |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/10/heroic-giffords-intern-co_n_806999.html |title=Heroic Giffords Intern Could Be Asked For Papers Under Arizona Immigration Law |journal=Huffington Post |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110111002538/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/10/heroic-giffords-intern-co_n_806999.html |archivedate=2011-01-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。吉福兹被送往大学医疗中心时情况非常危急<ref name="azcentral2011-01-08-optimistic" /><ref name="WP-20110109-killed">{{cite news |last=Murray |first=Shailagh |coauthors=Horwitz, Sari |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/08/AR2011010802422.html |title=Hospital: Rep. Gabrielle Giffords shot in Tucson rampage; federal judge killed |date=2011-01-09 |newspaper=The Washington Post |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216044622/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/08/AR2011010802422.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但神智仍然清醒。38分钟后<ref name="CNN-20110110-survive">{{cite news |last=Gupta |first=Sanjay |title=Gupta: What helped Giffords survive brain shot |date=2011-01-10 |publisher=CNN |url=http://thechart.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/10/gupta-how-giffords-survived-bullet-to-the-brain/ |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401155959/http://thechart.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/10/gupta-how-giffords-survived-bullet-to-the-brain/ |archivedate=2013-04-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，吉福兹开始接受紧急手术<ref name="WP-20110109-hope">{{cite news |last=Stein |first=Rob |coauthors=Vedantam, Shankar |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/09/AR2011010904439.html |title=Doctors see signs of hope for Giffords's recovery |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203151717/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/01/09/AR2011010904439.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，医生移除了她的部分头骨以免对[[大脑|大脑]]产生进一步损伤<ref name="CNN-20110110-survive" />。医生之后令她进入药物晕迷状态，以便大脑可以休息<ref name="ABC-20110109-coma">{{cite news |last=Carollo |first=Kim |title=Gabrielle Giffords in Medically Induced Coma to Help Brain Rest |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Health/gabrielle-giffords-health-update/story?id=12576433 |publisher=ABC News |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131134239/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/gabrielle-giffords-health-update/story?id=12576433 |archivedate=2013-01-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在1月12日的一次纪念仪式上，总统贝拉克·奥巴马宣布当天早些时候吉福兹已经自枪击事件后第一次睁开了眼睛<ref name="NYT_Cooper_20110112">{{cite news |last1=Cooper |first1=Helene |last2=Zeleny |first2=Jeff |title=Obama Calls for a New Era of Civility in U.S. Politics |date=2011-01-12 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13obama.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501131832/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13obama.html |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

随着情况得到改善，吉福兹开始了简单的物理治疗<ref name="ADW-20110114-therapy">{{cite news |last=Money |first=Luke |url=http://wildcat.arizona.edu/news/giffords-can-move-legs-begins-physical-therapy-1.1843099 |title=Giffords can move legs, begins physical therapy |newspaper=Arizona Daily Wildcat |date=2011-01-14 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110117041554/http://wildcat.arizona.edu/news/giffords-can-move-legs-begins-physical-therapy-1.1843099 |archivedate=2011-01-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2011年1月21日，枪击事件不到两星期后，她的情况已经足够稳定，[[休斯顿|休斯顿]]的[[赫尔曼纪念医疗系统|赫尔曼纪念医疗中心]]允许她出院。几天后，她被转移到中心的康复和研究学院接受物理治疗和康复方案治疗<ref name="CNN-20110121-transfer">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/21/arizona.shooting/index.html |title=Giffords arrives in Houston |last=Martinez |first=Michael |date=2011-01-21 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622234438/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/21/arizona.shooting/index.html }}</ref><ref name="CNN-Cohen-26Jan">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-01-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131150607/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/26/arizona.shooting.giffords/index.html?hpt=T1 |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/26/arizona.shooting.giffords/index.html?hpt=T1 |title=Giffords moves to rehabilitation hospital |last=Cohen |first=Elizabeth |date=2011-01-26 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>。经过检查，她休斯顿的医生感到乐观，称吉福兹的“康复潜力巨大”<ref name="AZStar-20110121-potential">{{cite news |url=http://azstarnet.com/news/local/article_4dc188e0-25a8-11e0-aa8e-001cc4c002e0.html |title=Doctor: Giffords has 'great rehabilitation potential' |date=2011-01-21 |newspaper=Arizona Daily Star |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2011-01-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110124194124/http://azstarnet.com/news/local/article_4dc188e0-25a8-11e0-aa8e-001cc4c002e0.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。医疗专家估计吉福兹的康复需要数月到超过一年的时间<ref name="CNN-20110111-injury">{{cite news |last=Landau |first=Elizabeth |archivedate=2013-01-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131151116/http://www.cnn.com/2011/HEALTH/01/11/giffords.brain.surgery/ |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/HEALTH/01/11/giffords.brain.surgery/ |title=Giffords in key period after brain injury |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-10-06 }}</ref>。

2011年8月1日，吉福兹于事发后首度在公共场所露面，她出现在联邦众议院为[[美國債務上限危機|提高债务上限]]投支持票。其他议员对她的出现起立致敬并鼓掌<ref name="congressreturnCNN">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/POLITICS/08/01/congress.giffords/index.html |title=Giffords returns to House for debt vote |date=2011-08-01 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archivedate=2013-01-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131151541/http://www.cnn.com/2011/POLITICS/08/01/congress.giffords/index.html }}</ref>。从10月25日到11月4日，吉福兹在[[阿什维尔|阿什维尔]]接受强化康复治疗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/10/23/us/north-carolina-giffords-rehab/index.html?_s=PM:US |title=Gabrielle Giffords to undergo 'intensive' therapy in North Carolina |publisher=CNN |date=2011-10-23 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120809183716/http://articles.cnn.com/2011-10-23/us/us_north-carolina-giffords-rehab_1_gabrielle-giffords-jared-loughner-intensive-therapy?_s=PM%3AUS |archivedate=2012-08-09 }}</ref>。2011年，她的[[丈夫|丈夫]][[马克·凯利|马克·凯利]]（{{lang|en|Mark Kelly}}）出版了一本回忆录：《盖比：一个勇气和希望的故事》（{{lang|en|''Gabby: A Story of Courage and Hope''}}，盖比是加布里埃尔的昵称），其中将吉福兹也列为作者之一。他在书中写道，虽然需要继续在语言能力上努力，并且双眼都已经失去了50%的视力，吉福兹仍然发誓要重返国会<ref>{{cite news |last1=Myers |first1=Amanda Lee |first2=Michelle |last2=Price |url=http://news.yahoo.com/ap-exclusive-giffords-vows-return-congress-154211434.html |title=AP Exclusive: Giffords vows return to Congress |publisher=Yahoo! |agency=Associated Press |date=2011-11-04 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010012/http://news.yahoo.com/ap-exclusive-giffords-vows-return-congress-154211434.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年1月22日，吉福兹宣布将辞去国会职务专心疗养，但也承诺将来会回归公共服务事业<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2012/01/22/giffords-to-resign-from-congress/ |title=Giffords to resign from Congress |publisher=Fox News Channel |accessdate=2013-10-07 |date=2012-01-22 |archivedate=2013-04-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401232622/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2012/01/22/giffords-to-resign-from-congress/ }}</ref>。她于1月25日在联邦众议院楼层递交了辞呈，众议院的同僚和领导层向她的勇气和力量致敬<ref name="LATfarewell">{{cite news |archivedate=2012-01-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126055707/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-na-giffords-bill-20120126%2C0%2C6404241.story |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-na-giffords-bill-20120126,0,6404241.story |title=Rep. Gabrielle Giffords sees her last bill pass, says farewell |last=Mascaro |first=Lisa |date=2012-01-26 |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2012-01-26 }}</ref>。

==调查==
[[File:Gabrielle_Giffords_shooting_scene_B.jpg|thumb]]
犯罪嫌疑人贾里德·李·劳纳据形容是一名约25岁左右的白人男性，短发，“穿着寒酸”。他被旁观众者拘留后再由警方逮捕<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" /><ref name="MSNBC-20110108">{{cite news |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/40980334/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ |title=Profile of Jared Loughner: 'I can't trust the current government' |publisher=MSNBC |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127053854/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/40980334/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ |archivedate=2013-01-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Reuters-20110108">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-05-02 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/08/us-usa-shooting-congresswoman-idUSTRE7071IA20110108 |deadurl=no |title=Congresswoman Gabrielle Giffords shot in Arizona |agency=Reuters |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |first=Roberta |last=Rampton |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502053621/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/08/us-usa-shooting-congresswoman-idUSTRE7071IA20110108 }}</ref>，警方之后公布了他的姓名和细节信息<ref name="MSNBC-20110108" />。[[联邦调查局|FBI]]试图讯问劳纳，但报道称他拒绝合作，援引了自己的[[美國憲法第五修正案|第五修正案]]权利<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" /><ref name="CNN2011-01-08" /><ref name="newstime">{{Cite news|url=http://www.newstime.co.za/WorldNews/Loughner_Invoking_Fifth_Amendment_After_Arizona_Slaughter/18361/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050128/http://www.newstime.co.za/WorldNews/Loughner_Invoking_Fifth_Amendment_After_Arizona_Slaughter/18361/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2016-03-04|title=Loughner Invoking Fifth Amendment After Arizona Slaughter|date=2011-01-09|accessdate=2011-01-09|work=NewsTime|agency=South African Press Association|location=New Zealand}}</ref>。当局称劳纳的动机尚不清楚<ref name="CNN2011-01-08" />，他们在劳纳家中的保险箱里发现了一些证据，其中包括一个信封上所写的注释，如“我提前做好计划”、“我的暗杀”和“吉福兹”，还有一封吉福兹办公室写来的信，感谢劳纳于2007年出席一个类似活动<ref name="I planned" /><ref>{{cite news |author=Nick Allen |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/8249720/Gabrielle-Giffords-shooting-Jared-Lee-Loughner-facing-five-charges.html |title=Gabrielle Giffords shooting: Jared Lee Loughner facing five charges |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430085409/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/8249720/Gabrielle-Giffords-shooting-Jared-Lee-Loughner-facing-five-charges.html |archivedate=2011-04-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

联邦政府官员于次日以杀害联邦政府雇员、试图刺杀国会议员和试图杀害联邦政府雇员的罪名起诉劳纳<ref name="P2">{{cite news |title=Federal charges could carry death penalty |accessdate=2013-10-07 |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0111/47298.html |work=Politico |date=2011-01-09 |author=Alexander Burns & Matt Negrin |archive-date=2013-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310162653/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0111/47298.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MSNBC2">{{cite news |title=Suspect charged in congresswoman's attack |archivedate=2012-11-04 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/40988567/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ |publisher=MSNBC |agency=Associated Press |date=2011-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104160541/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/40988567/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ |accessdate=2013-10-07 }}</ref><ref name="Reuters3">{{cite news |title=Suspect charged with attempted assassination of Giffords |accessdate=2013-10-07 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/10/us-usa-shooting-congresswoman-idUSTRE7071IA20110110 |agency=Reuters |date=2011-01-09 |author=Tim Gaynor and Peter Henderson |archivedate=2011-02-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226233639/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/10/us-usa-shooting-congresswoman-idUSTRE7071IA20110110 }}</ref>。警方报告显示他先通过了联邦调查局要求的背景检查后，于事发前不到六周在一家[[运动员仓库|运动员仓库]]（{{lang|en|Sportsman's Warehouse}}）商店购买了一支格洛克手枪<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-06-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613213423/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2011/01/09/arizona-suspected-gunman-no-stranger-to-trouble/ |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2011/01/09/arizona-suspected-gunman-no-stranger-to-trouble/ |title=Arizona Suspected Gunman Passed FBI Background Check |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-07 }}</ref>，并且当天早上还试图从一家[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]购买额外的弹药<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-11/glock-pistol-sales-surge-in-aftermath-of-shooting-of-arizona-s-giffords.html |title=Glock Pistol Sales Surge in Aftermath of Arizona Shootings |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |work=Bloomberg |first=Michael |last=Riley |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112052242/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-11/glock-pistol-sales-surge-in-aftermath-of-shooting-of-arizona-s-giffords.html |archivedate=2011-01-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但店员因觉得他形迹可疑而拒绝卖给他<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/09/arizona.shooting.investigation/index.html |title=Massacre suspect "mentally disturbed," former teacher says |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |publisher=CNN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110113000453/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/09/arizona.shooting.investigation/index.html |archivedate=2011-01-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703779704576074080255720732.html |title=Suspect Bought Bullets Hours Before Rampage |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |first=Evan |last=Perez |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110125192345/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703779704576074080255720732.html |archivedate=2011-01-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

由于枪击事件发生在图森市外的非建制区卡萨斯阿道比斯，因此[[皮马县|皮马县]]治安部门在[[图森警察局|图森警察局]]（{{lang|en|Tucson Police Department}}）和[[亚利桑那州公共安全部|亚利桑那州公共安全部]]（{{lang|en|Arizona Department of Public Safety}}）的协助下展开了初步调查<ref>CNN live broadcast</ref>。总统奥巴马派[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]局长[[羅伯特·米勒|羅伯特·米勒]]前往当地，而该局已经开始接手调查工作<ref>{{cite web |last=Spotts |first=Pete |title=Arizona shooting: Rep. Gabrielle Giffords hit at meeting with constituents |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/2011/0108/Arizona-shooting-Rep.-Gabrielle-Giffords-hit-at-meeting-with-constituents |work=The Christian Science Monitor |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923020718/http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/2011/0108/Arizona-shooting-Rep.-Gabrielle-Giffords-hit-at-meeting-with-constituents |archivedate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[美国国会警察|美国国会警察]]也展开了一轮调查<ref name="LaceyHerszenhorn2011-01-09" />。

===肇事者===
[[File:Jared_Loughner_USMS.jpg|thumb]]所拍劳纳的照片]]
贾里德·李·劳纳是一位22岁的白人男子，与双亲兰迪·劳纳和艾米·劳纳一起住在图森<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08">{{cite news |last=Lipton |first=Eric |last2=Savage |first2=Charlie |last3=Shane |first3=Scott |title=Arizona Suspect's Recent Acts Offer Hints of Alienation |date=2011-01-08 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09shooter.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528152221/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09shooter.html |archivedate=2013-05-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，距案发地点约8[[公里|公里]]<ref name="MSNBC-20110108" /><ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" />。他的母亲为城市公园部门工作，父亲的职业未知<ref name="JohnsonKirk2011-01-09">{{cite news |last=Johnson |first=Kirk |coauthors=Serge F. Kovaleski, Dan Frosch, Eric Lipton |title=Jared L. Loughner's Odd Behavior Caused Alarm |date=2011-01-09 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10shooter.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409165205/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10shooter.html |archivedate=2013-04-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。劳纳曾就读[[皮马社区学院|皮马社区学院]]（{{lang|en|Pima Community College}}），他的老同学称劳纳当时学习认真，渴求知识<ref name="JohnsonKirk2011-01-09" />。因为教师和同学对劳纳在课堂上越来越多的破坏性行为进行投诉，学校于2010年9月29日暂停了他的学业，他于10月退学<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="JohnsonKirk2011-01-09" />。由于学院要求他先做重新入学的[[心理健康|心理健康]]（{{lang|en|mental health}}）评估，劳纳决定不再返校<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="JohnsonKirk2011-01-09" />。

枪击事件前，劳纳已有过两项罪行，其中一项是持有毒品<ref name="Swaine2011-01-08">{{cite news |last=Swaine |first=Jon |title=Gabrielle Giffords shooting: strange internet trail of 'loner' Jared Lee Loughner, the alleged Tucson gunman |date=2011-01-08 |newspaper=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/8248692/Gabrielle-Giffords-shooting-strange-internet-trail-of-loner-Jared-Lee-Loughner-the-alleged-Tucson-gunman.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808205107/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/8248692/Gabrielle-Giffords-shooting-strange-internet-trail-of-loner-Jared-Lee-Loughner-the-alleged-Tucson-gunman.html |archivedate=2012-08-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他已经开始对吉福兹念念不忘<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-06-14 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0112/71169.html |title=Gabrielle Giffords' future is up in the air a year after Tucson shooting |first=Jonathan |last=Allen |work=Politico |date=2012-01-06 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614003234/http://www.politico.com//news/stories/0112/71169.html }}</ref>，并曾参加过2007年8月在图森一家商场举行的“国会在你这边”活动，与吉福兹见过面<ref name="WSJ_20110110">{{cite news |last=Emshwiller |first=John R. |last2=Barrett |first2=Devlin |last3=Forrelle |first3=Charles |title=Suspect Fixated on Giffords |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2011-01-10 |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703667904576071191163461466.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130924210328/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703667904576071191163461466.html |archivedate=2013-09-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]官员称劳纳曾于2008年申请入伍，但这一申请因“不合格”而遭拒<ref name="JohnsonKirk2011-01-09" />。由于保密方面规定，他们拒绝作进一步披露<ref name="MSNBC-20110108" /><ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="AZStar-20110108">{{cite news |last=Steller |first=Tim |url=http://azstarnet.com/news/local/crime/article_91db5db4-1b74-11e0-ba23-001cc4c002e0.html |title=Man linked to Giffords shooting called 'very disturbed' |newspaper=Arizona Daily Star |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731045111/http://azstarnet.com/news/local/crime/article_91db5db4-1b74-11e0-ba23-001cc4c002e0.html |archivedate=2012-07-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。一位政府官员向媒体透露，劳纳是在一项毒品测试上没有通过<ref name="CNN_20110110">{{cite news |last=Griffin |first=Drew |last2=Yellin |first2=Jessica |last3=Candiotti |first3=Susan |last4=Bash |first4=Dana |last5=Rowlands |first5=Ted |last6=Meserve |first6=Jeanne |last7=Silverleib |first7=Alan |last8=Wian |first8=Casey |last9=Bohn |first9=Kevin |display-authors=5 |title=Giffords stabilizes as suspect heads to court |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-11 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/10/arizona.shooting/index.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110301074203/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/10/arizona.shooting/index.html |archivedate=2011-03-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

劳纳已经使用{{lang|en|Myspace}}和{{lang|en|YouTube}}账号“{{lang|en|Classitup10}}”在线上发布了一段时间的信息<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="CNN_Pima_County_Sheriff">{{cite news |title=Arizona massacre suspect: 'Kind of a troubled past' |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-09 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023083828/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/08/arizona.shooting.suspect/ |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/08/arizona.shooting.suspect/ |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref><ref name="Grinberg2011-01-08">{{cite news |last=Grinberg |first=Emanuella |title=Witness: Arizona gunman 'was ready for war' |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-08 |url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/08/several-people-shot-at-arizona-store-police-official-says/ |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511003104/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/08/several-people-shot-at-arizona-store-police-official-says/ |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，表达了自己对[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]、联邦法律的看法，表示他相信政府在对公民进行洗脑<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="Swaine2011-01-08" /><ref name="Grinberg2011-01-08" /><ref name="upi">{{cite news |url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2011/01/08/Loughner-mused-if-he-was-a-terrorist/UPI-44681294537795/ |title=Loughner mused if he was a terrorist |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |agency=United Press International |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022064138/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2011/01/08/Loughner-mused-if-he-was-a-terrorist/UPI-44681294537795/ |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。枪击发生前数小时，劳纳的{{lang|en|Myspace}}页面进行了更新，他的账户发布了一条这样的信息：“再见”，并且对好友们说：“请别生我的气。”<ref name="Lipton2011-01-08" /><ref name="Slate">{{cite web |last=Shafer |first=Jack |last2=Tapper |first2=Jake |last3=Balko |first3=Radley |last4=Marshall |first4=Josh |last5=Smith |first5=Ben |last6=Kirn |first6=Walter |last7=Lithwick |first7=Dahlia |last8=Maddow |first8=Rachel |last9=Davis |first9=Susan |displayauthors=9 |title=The Giffords Shooting |work=Slate |date=2011-01-08 |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/press_box/2011/01/the_giffords_shooting.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026041521/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/press_box/2011/01/the_giffords_shooting.html |archivedate=2012-10-26 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref><ref name="Weisenthal">{{cite news |last=Weisenthal |first=Joe |title=Gunman Identified As Jared Lee Loughner |work=Business Insider |date=2011-01-08 |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/jared-lee-loughner-2011-1 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531211234/http://www.businessinsider.com/jared-lee-loughner-2011-1 |archivedate=2013-05-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

有报道称，枪击发生当天早些时候，劳纳因为从汽车后备箱取出一个黑色的包裹而与父亲发生了争执<ref name="ABCNewsUS">{{cite web |last=Banfield |first=Ashleigh |coauthors=Jessica Hopper; Josey Crews; Emily Friedman |title=Tucson Shooting: Jared Loughner Stopped for Traffic Violation Hours Before Shooting |publisher=ABC News |date=2011-01-12 |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/tucson-shooting-jared-loughner-stopped-authorities-hours-shooting/story?id=12597092 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923053116/http://abcnews.go.com/US/tucson-shooting-jared-loughner-stopped-authorities-hours-shooting/story?id=12597092 |archivedate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这个包裹与之后在附近沙漠里找到的一个装有9毫米弹药，被认为属于劳纳的包裹描述相述<ref name="FOX11AZ">{{cite web |last=Fox 11 |title=Loughner's black bag found |publisher=KMSB-TV |date=2011-01-14 |archivedate=2011-09-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928222914/http://www.fox11az.com/news/local/Loughners-black-bag-found-113613454.html |url=http://www.fox11az.com/news/local/Loughners-black-bag-found-113613454.html |accessdate=2011-09-28 }}</ref>。当天早上约7:30，劳纳因闯红灯而被[[亚利桑那州渔猎部|亚利桑那州渔猎部]]（{{lang|en|Arizona Game and Fish Department}}）人员拦下，但他们认为劳纳并没有什么明显的威胁，所以只给了一个提醒就放他走了<ref name="ABCNewsUS" />。

===法律诉讼===
[[File:FCI_Phoenix.jpg|thumb]]

劳纳曾被关押在凤凰城联邦惩戒所（{{lang|en|Federal Correctional Institution, Phoenix}}），不得保释<ref name="BOP-locator" /><ref name="ABC15-20110109-held">{{cite news |title=Tucson shooting suspect held without bail |url=http://www.abc15.com/dpp/news/national/suspect-jared-loughner-faces-federal-charges-in-tucson-shooting |publisher=KNXV-TV |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112081408/http://www.abc15.com/dpp/news/national/suspect-jared-loughner-faces-federal-charges-in-tucson-shooting |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。所有亚利桑那州法官均在本案中采取回避，因为法官约翰·罗尔也在这起事件中被杀<ref name="USAToday-20110111-recusal">{{cite news |last=Johnson |first=Kevin |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/washington/2011-01-12-defense12_ST_N.htm |title=In Loughner case, Ariz. federal judiciary considers recusal |newspaper=USA Today |date=2011-01-11 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103172836/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/washington/2011-01-12-defense12_ST_N.htm }}</ref><ref name="CNN-20110112-lawyer">{{cite news |last=O'Neill |first=Ann |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/12/arizona.judy.clarke.profile/ |title=Lawyer keeps even the most loathed criminals off death row |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120074408/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/01/12/arizona.judy.clarke.profile/ |archivedate=2011-01-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这起联邦案件被分配给来自位于[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|圣地牙哥]][[美国加利福尼亚南部联邦地区法院|美国加利福尼亚南部联邦地区法院]]的联邦法官[[拉里·艾伦·伯恩斯|拉里·艾伦·伯恩斯]]（{{lang|en|Larry Alan Burns}}）审理<ref>{{cite journal |archivedate=2012-12-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121209105704/http://tpmmuckraker.talkingpointsmemo.com/2011/01/due_to_arizona_conflicts_california_judge_takes_ov.php |url=http://talkingpointsmemo.com/muckraker/due-to-arizona-conflicts-california-judge-takes-over-loughner-case |title=Due To Arizona Conflicts, California Judge Takes Over Loughner Case |last=Reilly |first=Ryan J. |journal=Talking Points Memo |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。而同样在圣地牙哥的[[公共辩护律师|公共辩护律师]]（{{lang|en|public defender}}）[[朱迪·克拉克|朱迪·克拉克]]（{{lang|en|Judy Clarke}}）被派为劳纳在联邦法庭上的辩护律师<ref>{{cite news |last=Hoffer |first=Steven |title=Judy Clarke, Who Defended the 'Unabomber,' Will Represent Jared Lee Loughner |work=AOL News |publisher=AOL |date=2011-01-10 |archivedate=2013-05-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507040429/http://www.aolnews.com/2011/01/10/judy-clarke-who-defended-the-unabomber-will-represent-jared/ |url=http://www.aolnews.com/2011/01/10/judy-clarke-who-defended-the-unabomber-will-represent-jared/ |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/11/us/11defender.html?_r=0 |title=Loughner's Lawyer Is Called a Master Strategist |author=William Glaberson |work=The New York Times |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130711201537/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/11/us/11defender.html |archivedate=2013-07-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2011年1月19日，一个联邦[[大陪审团|大陪审团]]决定以三项罪名起诉劳纳，分别是试图刺案众议员吉福兹和试图杀害两位联邦雇员，即吉福兹的助手[[罗恩·巴伯|罗恩·巴伯]]（{{lang|en|Ron Barber}}）和帕梅拉·西蒙（{{lang|en|Pamela Simon}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jan/20/nation/la-na-0120-loughner-indictment-20110120 |title=Federal grand jury indicts Loughner in Giffords shooting |last=Riccardi |first=Nicholas |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-01-20 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105033056/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jan/20/nation/la-na-0120-loughner-indictment-20110120 |archivedate=2012-11-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。3月3日，劳纳还受到了谋杀和预谋杀人等多项起诉，控罪数量共达49项<ref name="CNN-20110304-indicted">{{cite news |last=Cratty and |first=Carol |archivedate=2011-03-07 |deadurl=no |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/03/04/arizona.loughner/ |title=Alleged Tucson gunman indicted on 49 charges in shooting |publisher=CNN |date=2011-03-04 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307093921/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/03/04/arizona.loughner/ }}</ref>。

亚利桑那州检察官代表不是联邦雇员的受害者发起谋杀和预谋杀人的指控。根据该州的[[迅速审判条款|迅速审判]]法规，州检察官通常从嫌犯被捕后有10天的时间来提出起诉，但嫌犯被联邦部门关押的时间不予计入。劳纳无论是在联邦还是州法院被定罪，都有可能面临[[死刑|死刑]]的惩罚。<ref>{{cite web |last=Smith |first=Kim |title=LaWall considers state charges in Tucson shooting spree case |work=Arizona Daily Star |date=2011-01-10 |archivedate=2011-01-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110111174226/http://azstarnet.com/news/local/crime/article_73b56d54-1ce4-11e0-8c0e-001cc4c002e0.html |url=http://azstarnet.com/news/local/crime/article_73b56d54-1ce4-11e0-8c0e-001cc4c002e0.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>

2011年5月25日，伯恩斯法官根据两份医疗评估认为劳纳不能上法庭受审，这份报告认为后者患有偏执精神分裂症<ref name="competence" />，法官随后下令对劳纳进行强制治疗<ref>{{cite web |title=Trial not likely for Jared Lee Loughner in 2012 |url=http://nypost.com/2012/01/06/trial-not-likely-for-jared-lee-loughner-in-2012/ |work=New York Post |accessdate=2013-10-09 |agency=Associated Press |date=2012-01-06 |archivedate=2012-04-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410155157/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/national/trial_not_likely_for_jared_lee_loughner_NHbkr1Kh2Dmr2gxvFMq48M }}</ref>。2012年1月25日，法官下令对嫌犯的心理状况进行新一轮评估<ref>{{cite news |url=http://azstarnet.com/news/local/new-loughner-evaluation-due-jan/article_913b6b9c-69a0-5e98-94dd-b885d2fb932c.html |title=New Loughner evaluation due Jan. 25 |publisher=Arizona Daily Star |date=2012-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118072657/http://azstarnet.com/news/local/new-loughner-evaluation-due-jan/article_913b6b9c-69a0-5e98-94dd-b885d2fb932c.html |archivedate=2012-01-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2012年2月6日，劳纳在[[密苏里州|密苏里州]][[斯普林菲尔德_(密苏里州)|斯普林菲尔德]]关押的时间被延长4个月<ref>{{cite web |title=U.S. judge grants more time for accused Tucson shooter |archivedate=2012-11-13 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/07/us-usa-shooting-tucson-idUSTRE81525R20120207 |agency=Reuters |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113010024/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/07/us-usa-shooting-tucson-idUSTRE81525R20120207 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |date=2012-02-06 }}</ref>。劳纳的律师请求停止对他的当事人强制用药，但受到了拒绝<ref>{{cite web |title=Jared Lee Loughner Loses 3 Appeals Over Forced Medication |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/05/jared-lee-loughner-trial-forced-medication-arizona-shooting_n_1321407.html |work=Huffington Post |accessdate=2013-10-09 |agency=Associated Press |date=2012-03-05 |archivedate=2013-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630055205/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/05/jared-lee-loughner-trial-forced-medication-arizona-shooting_n_1321407.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。原计划于2012年6月27日举行的受审能力听证会之后予以改期<ref>{{cite web |last=Jennifer |first=Bowen |title=Hearing set to determine if alleged Tucson shooter can stand trial |url=http://www.tucsonnewsnow.com/story/18617846/hearing-set-to-determine-if-alleged-tucson-shooter-can-stand-trial |publisher=Tucson News Now |accessdate=2013-10-09 |date=2012-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009085733/http://www.tucsonnewsnow.com/story/18617846/hearing-set-to-determine-if-alleged-tucson-shooter-can-stand-trial |archive-date=2013-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=David |first=Schwartz |title=Accused Tucson shooter's competency hearing rescheduled |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022204412/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/12/us-usa-shooting-loughner-idUSBRE85B1IJ20120612 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/12/us-usa-shooting-loughner-idUSBRE85B1IJ20120612 |agency=Reuters |accessdate=2012-07-16 |date=2012-06-12 }}</ref>。

2012年8月7日，[[法医心理学家|法医心理学家]]（{{lang|en|forensic psychologist}}）克里斯蒂娜·皮耶兹博士（{{lang|en|Dr. Christina Pietz}}）在劳纳的受审能力听证会上作证，表示自己相信劳纳可以接受法庭审判，法官伯恩斯于是判决劳纳有能力受审。劳纳随后对19项指控予以认罪，因此逃过了死刑的惩罚<ref>{{cite web |title=Jared Loughner is found competent to stand trial |url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/articles/20120807tucson-shooting-loughner-court-hearing.html |work=The Arizona Republic |accessdate=2013-10-09}}</ref>。

2012年11月8日，劳纳出现在法庭上接受量刑，多位被他杀害的受害者亲属也来到现场。法官伯恩斯判处劳纳连续7个无期徒刑加140年有期徒刑，且不得[[假释|假释]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Ball |first=James |title=Jared Lee Loughner sentenced to life in prison |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/gabrielle-giffords-confronts-shooter-jared-lee-loughner-in-court/2012/11/08/09968fe2-29c7-11e2-b4e0-346287b7e56c_story.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2012-11-08 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021054724/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/gabrielle-giffords-confronts-shooter-jared-lee-loughner-in-court/2012/11/08/09968fe2-29c7-11e2-b4e0-346287b7e56c_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Duke |first=Alan |title=Loughner sentenced to life for Arizona shootings |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/11/08/justice/arizona-loughner-sentencing/index.html |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-09 |date=2012-11-09 |archivedate=2012-11-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109141836/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/11/08/justice/arizona-loughner-sentencing/index.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Santos |first=Fernanda |title=Gunman in Giffords Shooting Sentenced to 7 Life Terms |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/09/us/gunman-who-shot-giffords-to-be-sentenced.html?ref=jaredleeloughner&_r=0 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2012-11-08 |archivedate=2013-04-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409165212/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/09/us/gunman-who-shot-giffords-to-be-sentenced.html?ref=jaredleeloughner&_r=0 }}</ref>。

