Naman |first=Christine Pisera |year=2002 |publisher=Health Communications, Inc |location=Deerfield Beach, Florida |isbn=0-7573-0097-9 |page=41 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=VayUKdTuI7kC&pg=PA41 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archive-date=2016-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429223431/https://books.google.com/books?id=VayUKdTuI7kC&pg=PA41 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她是前[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]球员、投手兼经理[[达拉斯·格林|达拉斯·格林]]（{{lang|en|Dallas Green}}）的孙女儿，也是女演员[[蘇菲亞·布希|蘇菲亞·布希]]的表妹<ref name="NYT_Berger" /><ref>{{cite news |first=Joe |last=Posnanski |title=A Death in The Family |date=2011-01-24 |work=Sports Illustrated |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1180934/index.htm |quote=Everyone says Christina had Roxanna's grace and John's spirit. |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archivedate=2012-11-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103203709/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1180934/index.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>；
