==反应==
===政治===
枪击事件发生后，民主党和共和党都呼吁对恶劣的政治辞令降温，回归[[两党合作|两党合作]]（{{lang|en|bipartisanship}}）<ref name="rhetoric" />。事件发生前一天晚上，吉福兹给自己的朋友，[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]州务卿，共和党人[[特雷·格雷森|特雷·格雷森]]（{{lang|en|Trey Grayson}}）写了封信，称“我们需要想办法给政治辞令和党派之争降降温”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://talkingpointsmemo.com/dc/giffords-sent-email-on-eve-of-shooting-calling-for-toned-down-rhetoric?ref=tn |title=Giffords Sent Email on Eve of Shooting Calling For Toned Down Rhetoric |first=Eric |last=Lack |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |work=Talking Points Memo |archivedate=2012-12-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121209080427/http://tpmdc.talkingpointsmemo.com/2011/01/giffords-sent-email-on-eve-of-shooting-calling-for-toned-down-rhetoric.php?ref=tn }}</ref>。2010年3月，吉福兹曾对莎拉·佩林的[[竞选|竞选]]网页上有针对性地用十字光标瞄准[[2010年美國中期選舉|全国中期选举]]上部分国会席位的做法表示担忧，这其中吉福兹所在的亚历桑那州第八国会选区就赫然在目。这张地图发布后，吉福兹的工作也于当月晚些时候受到了恶意的破坏，她表示：“我们在莎拉·佩林的‘目标’名单上，但问题在于，她是用枪瞄准器十字光标来表明自己的目标，但当人们真的这样做的话，他们需要意识到这类行径的后果。”不过在接受一次采访时，她又称：“竞选演说和战争言辞多年来就已经可以互换了。”<ref name="Quinn-Gallagher-2011-01-09" /><ref name="nyt-vitriol" />枪击事件发生后，佩林的网站上撤除了这张图片<ref name="nyt-vitriol">{{cite news |title=Bloodshed Puts New Focus on Vitriol in Politics |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09capital.html?_r=0 |author=Carl Hulse |coauthors=Kate Zernike |accessdate=2013-10-09 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2011-01-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528152226/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/09/us/politics/09capital.html |archivedate=2013-05-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Coutsoukis |first=Photius |title=Screenshot of Sarah Palin's Facebook Page with the "Cross Hairs" Map |publisher=articlesurfing.org |archivedate=2013-01-21 |url=http://www.articlesurfing.org/politics_and_government/sarah_palin_facebook_reconstructed.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121022108/http://articlesurfing.org/politics_and_government/sarah_palin_facebook_reconstructed.html |deadurl=no |date=2011年1月 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-08-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828090742/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/09/advisor-linking-palin-to-shootings-appalling/ |url=http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/09/advisor-linking-palin-to-shootings-appalling/ |title=Adviser: Linking Palin to shootings 'appalling' |author=Mark Preston |publisher=CNN |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。佩林在1月12日的一段视频中回应了对她的批评，拒绝接受除枪手外的任何人应该对图森枪击事件负责的观点，并指责媒体制造“[[血液诽谤|血液诽谤]]”（{{lang|en|blood libel}}）来将这一事件怪罪到她和[[右派|右派]]的头上<ref name="NYT_Zeleny">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13palin.html?_r=0 |title=Palin Joins Debate on Heated Speech With Words That Stir New Controversy |first1=Jeff |last1=Zeleny |first2=Michael D. |last2=Shear |work=The New York Times |date=2011-01-12 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501120601/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/13palin.html |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="CNNbloodlibel">{{cite news |url=http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/12/palin-says-efforts-to-lay-blame-reprehensible/#more-142708 |title=Palin says efforts to lay blame 'reprehensible' and a 'blood libel' |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407102455/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/01/12/palin-says-efforts-to-lay-blame-reprehensible/#more-142708 |archivedate=2013-04-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2011/01/11/democrats-single-sharron-angle-calling-limits-speech/ |title=Palin Criticizes Manufacturers of 'Blood Libel' as Proponents of Speech Limits Cite Sharron Angle |publisher=Fox News Channel |date=2010-04-07 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026124614/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2011/01/11/democrats-single-sharron-angle-calling-limits-speech/ |archivedate=2012-10-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

一些观察家指出，美国，特别是亚利桑那州的政治气候可能对这一暴力行径存在促进因素。例如皮马县警长[[克拉伦斯·达普尼克|克拉伦斯·达普尼克]]（{{lang|en|Clarence Dupnik}}）起初曾表示对过激政治言论和暴力可能存在关联的担忧，他表示：“当你看着那些不平衡的人们，他们对一些嘴里所说出的有关打倒政府的言论有什么样的反应，那种愤怒、仇恨和偏执，正在这个国家变得越来越离谱。”他相信亚利桑那州已经不幸成为这类感觉的“首都”。称“我们已经成为偏见和偏执的圣地”<ref name="NYTimes-20110110-spotlight">{{cite news |archivedate=2013-04-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409165229/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10arizona.html?_r=1&src=twt&twt=nytimes |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/us/10arizona.html?_r=1&src=twt&twt=nytimes |title=Shooting Casts a Harsh Spotlight on Arizona's Unique Politics |first=Jennifer |last=Steinhauer |work=The New York Times |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/44/2011/01/sheriff-dupniks-criticism-of-p.html |title=Sheriff Dupnik's criticism of political 'vitriol' resonates with public |work=The Washington Post |author=Sandhya Somashekhar |date=2011-01-09 |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126110827/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/44/2011/01/sheriff-dupniks-criticism-of-p.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但达普尼克之后也表示自己没有任何证据表明劳纳是因自己看到或听到的任何特定内容而触发了这场杀戮<ref>{{cite news |last=Mirkinson |first=Jack |title=Megyn Kelly Debates Sheriff Clarence Dupnik About His Comments on Arizona Shooting (VIDEO) |work=Huffington Post |date=2011-01-09 |archivedate=2013-05-14 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/09/megyn-kelly-debates-clarence-dupnik_n_806521.html |accessdate=2013-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514062511/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/09/megyn-kelly-debates-clarence-dupnik_n_806521.html }}</ref>。国际媒体在相关报道中提及了美国的政治气候，特别是佩林的选举地图<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-12147588 |title=Shot US congresswoman Gabrielle Giffords 'doing well' |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2013-10-09 |date=2011-01-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927220200/http://www.