7221717/http://spectator.org/blog/2011/01/09/arizona-shootings-it-was-a-col |url=http://spectator.org/blog/2011/01/09/arizona-shootings-it-was-a-col |title=Arizona Shootings: 'It Was a Colossal Failure of Journalism' |work=The American Spectator |accessdate=2013-10-10 }}</ref>。[[保羅·克魯格曼|保羅·克魯格曼]]在[[社论对页版|社论对页版]]发表的一篇文章中认为政治辞令已经有了毒性<ref name="Krugman2011-01-09">{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Krugman |date=2011-01-09 |title=Climate of Hate |newspaper=The New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/opinion/10krugman.html |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501110753/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/10/opinion/10krugman.html |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。多位评论员在事件后重新呼吁淡化政治言辞的攻击性<ref name="Olbermann2011-01-08">{{cite news |last=Olbermann |first=Keith |title=Keith Olbermann Issues Special Comment on Arizona Shooting: 'Violence Has No Place In Democracy' |date=2011-01-08 |work=Huffington Post |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/08/keith-olbermann-arizona-shooting_n_806311.html |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515045519/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/01/08/keith-olbermann-arizona-shooting_n_806311.html |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Minora2011-01-08">{{cite news |last=Minora |first=Leslie |title=Keith Olbermann Calls Out Conservatives for Inciting Tucson Shooting, Includes Allen West, Repents |date=2011-01-09 |work=Broward/Palm Beach New Times |publisher=New Times BPB |archivedate=2012-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723002025/http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/pulp/2011/01/tucson_shooting_gabrielle_giffords_olbermann.php |url=http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/pulp/2011/01/tucson_shooting_gabrielle_giffords_olbermann.php |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-10-10 }}</ref><ref name="Estes2011-01-11">{{cite web |last=Estes |first=Adam Clark |title=Jon Stewart on shooting: No idea how to process this |date=2011-01-11 |work=Salon |archivedate=2011-03-20 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.salon.com/2011/01/11/jon_stewart_arizona_shooting/ |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110320205435/http://www.salon.com/news/feature/2011/01/11/jon_stewart_arizona_shooting }}</ref>。[[基思·奥尔伯曼|基思·奥尔伯曼]]（{{lang|en|Keith Olbermann}}）对自己任何可能煸动暴力行为的言论道歉：“暴力或是威胁使用暴力都为我们的民主所不容，我为自己过去即使是无意鼓励了暴力的言行道歉，并将这样的言行推翻。”<ref name="Olbermann2011-01-08" />[[喬恩·史都華|喬恩·史都華]]表示，自己不知道政治环境是否对这起事件造成了什么促进性的影响，但是夸大其辞和泼[[硫酸|硫酸]]的做法已经成为如今政治程序中的一部分。当行为和这样的激烈言辞相匹配时，人们还是会感到恐惧，这或许有助于让大家记住要言行一致，把言辞和实际更多地联系起来<ref name="Estes2011-01-11" />。

===纪念===
[[File:Gabrielle_Giffords_shooting_scene_C.jpg|thumb]]

为了纪念图森枪击事件中的遇难者，总统奥巴马下令所有公共和军事场所从2011年1月9号起直至14号日落降半旗致哀<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wildcat.arizona.edu/article/2011/01/president_obama_orders_flags_flown_at_halfstaff_to_honor_arizona_shooting_victims |title=President Obama orders flags flown at half-staff to honor Arizona shooting victims |publisher=ARIZONA DAILY WILDCAT |work=DAILYWILDCAT.com |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502130106/http://www.wildcat.arizona.edu/article/2011/01/president_obama_orders_flags_flown_at_halfstaff_to_honor_arizona_shooting_victims |dead-url=no }}</ref>，多个州的州长也宣布执行了同类措施<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Governor+Rendell+Orders+Flags+Statewide+to+Fly+at+Half-Staff+in+Honor...-a0246101753 |title=Governor Rendell Orders Flags Statewide to Fly at Half-Staff in Honor of Arizona Shooting Victims |publisher=The Free Library |accessdate=2013-10-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://azgovernor.gov/HalfStaff.asp |title=ARIZONA HALF-STAFF INFORMATION CENTER |publisher=Official Website of Arizona State Governor Janice K. Brewer |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815032959/http://azgovernor.gov/HalfStaff.asp |archivedate=2013-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/governor-rendell-orders-flags-statewide-to-fly-at-half-staff-in-honor-of-arizona-shooting-victims-113198409.html |title=Governor Rendell Orders Flags Statewide to Fly at Half-Staff in Honor of Arizona Shooting Victims |publisher=Pennsylvania Office of the Governor |work=PR Newswire |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225143033/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/governor-rendell-orders-flags-statewide-to-fly-at-half-staff-in-honor-of-arizona-shooting-victims-113198409.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年1月10日[[北美东部时区|EST]]上午11点，[[白宫南草坪|白宫南草坪]]和[[美國國會大廈|国会大厦]]的台阶上举行了全国性的默哀仪式<ref>{{cite news |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/onpolitics/post/2011/01/congress-moment-of-silence-gabrielle-giffords-/1 |title=Moment of silence observed on Capitol steps |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Co. Inc |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |first=Catalina |last=Camia |archivedate=2012-10-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005134958/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/onpolitics/post/2011/01/congress-moment-of-silence-gabrielle-giffords-/1 }}</ref>。奥巴马于1月12日来到图森面见了受害者家属，并到医疗中心看望了还躺在床上的吉福兹，当晚又通过电视直播发表了[[贝拉克·奥巴马图森枪击事件纪念演讲|纪念演说]]<ref name="Obama-NYT-2011-01-12">{{cite news |last=Obama |first=Barack |title=Obama's Remarks in Tucson |date=2011-01-12 |newspaper=The New York Times |issn=0362-4331 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/politics/13obama-text.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501114300/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/13/us/politics/13obama-text.html |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

事件发生地点的西夫弗商品之后重新开业时，工作人员搭建了一个临时性的纪念场所<ref name="Safeway" />；[[2011年美国职棒大联盟全明星赛|2011年美国职棒大联盟全明星赛]]上，吉福兹的实习生小丹尼尔·埃尔南德斯由受害者亲属陪同一起来到球场上，投出了纪念性的第一球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/nov/10/nation/la-na-daniel-hernandez-20111110 |title=Former Giffords intern elected to Arizona school board |date=2011-11-10 |first=Ashley |last=Powers |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archivedate=2012-10-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015170706/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/nov/10/nation/la-na-daniel-hernandez-20111110 }}</ref>；[[2011年国情咨文|2011年国情咨文演讲]]时，来自[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]的[[联邦参议员|联邦参议员]][[马克·尤德尔|马克·尤德尔]]提议两院议员不分党派坐到一起，留下一个空座位来向吉福兹致敬<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/itsallpolitics/2011/01/13/132888876/sen-udall-urges-bipartisan-seating-for-state-of-union |title=Bipartisan State of Union Seating Urged By Sen. Mark Udall |publisher=NPR |date=2011-01-13 |accessdate=2013-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121202082730/http://www.npr.org/blogs/itsallpolitics/2011/01/13/132888876/sen-udall-urges-bipartisan-seating-for-state-of-union |archivedate=2012-12-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

